# Cockatoo Gateway

Cockatoo Gateway is a simple gateway that forwards requests to a specified backend microservice.

## Docker

To build an image run ``docker build -t cockatoo-gateway .`` from ``./CockatooGateway/``.

To run the image, run ```docker run -d -p 5000:5000 --name cockatoo-gateway cockatoo-gateway``.

You can also run this together by executing the following command:

```docker build -t cockatoo-gateway .
docker run -d -p 5000:5000 --name cockatoo-gateway cockatoo-gateway```
